537
00:38:03,678 --> 00:38:05,659
J'ai laissé ton... dans le...

538
00:38:05,917 --> 00:38:06,911
Excellent.

539
00:38:08,712 --> 00:38:09,828
Pour la route ?

540
00:38:10,494 --> 00:38:11,494
D'accord.

541
00:38:16,032 --> 00:38:16,940
Merci.

542
00:38:17,773 --> 00:38:20,380
- Appelle-moi quand ça arrive.
